metadata.name: Dead Serious #1
metadata.description: This unique NFT collectible is a reflection of how people on earth are suffering because of their own mistakes. Mother nature is boss and If human beings won't start NOW to respect the environment much worse things will happen soon. In my point of view this topic should be addressed more intensively in our every day life in order to start to live in harmony with mother nature. If not, mother nature will make us disappear very soon.
